Git Project Configuration

git config --global user.name "Astra-max" - Tells git about the username
git config --global user.email "waoremaxwel17@gmail.com" - Tells git about the user email

git config --global editor "code --wait" - Tells git the default editor
git config --global diff.tool code - Tells git about your preffered diff tool
git config --global diff.vscode.cmd "code --wait --diff $LOCAL $REMOTE" - Tells git how to launch the diff tool
